channel.title: Wtf? what does this mean
channel.description:
To see what i'm talking about, go to the ringtone picture on this page: [url=http://profile.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=user.viewprofile&friendID=154829889]Myspace for movie "one missed call"[/url]
on that picture for the ringtone, those little words, what exactly do they mean? it confuses the hell out of me.

item.title: Wtf? what does this mean
item.dc:creator: @ilyaostr9 io9
item.description:
@ilyaostr9 wrote:

It means that unless your cellular plan allows SMS (text messaging) and data transfer (GPRS, I presume), you’re gonna run up your cell phone bill.
